channel.description: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?omk5mjgzonm]Download Link - Click here! [/url] This is a 508 Client With Most things From 525. This is the Fathienblade Client v.4 With All Customs and All Java Files. You can change it and do anything. I am making a new source and decided to release the client to public. What does this have? Customs, New Tabs And Other Things. Customs: Music cape, Donator Cape, Death Cape, Owner Godsword, Twin sword, Dragon Godsword, Zaros Godsword, All Vesta, All Statius, Zuriel No Hood, Morrigans No Javelin, All Spirit Sheilds, Dragon Platebody, Abbysal Scythe, New models of Scimitar and Longsword, Dragon Claws, Granite Mace, Inferno Adze, All the statutte and Other PvP Drops. [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/t896w8.png[/img] If you like or hate, Please Comment On How i can improve it. Thanks.
